items.title: We need a canvas for input rather than textbox for all AI chatbots
items.summary: All the input textboxes on major ai chatbots like Gemini, chatgpt, claude are tiny, this deters us from writing elaborate prompts. We need to have an option/button which opens a canvas where we can write bigger prompts. If anyone who are building these are reading this, please consider this request. Comments URL: https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46155312 Points: 1 # Comments: 1
